@@TJvXPCustomButton.WordWrap
Summary
  Determines whether the control inserts soft carriage returns so text wraps at the right margin.
Description
  Use WordWrap to specify how the text is drawn when it doesn't fit inside the control. If WordWrap
  is true, the text will be wrapped to as many lines as needed to fit the text inside the control.
See Also
  <DELPHILINK TControl.Caption>

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
